she said&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What I want to say is
Every time I see you convert your ideals into action, it drives me forward.
It&amp;rsquo;s amazing. We obviously don&amp;rsquo;t contact each other very often.
So you have always been a friend that I am very proud of.
You will attract equally good people as you said in your writing.
Like me :D)&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>ROC Year 115, May 8th</title><link>https://ezrawu-tw.github.io/en/posts/0508/</link><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ezrawu-tw.github.io/en/posts/0508/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Read this today
